Crown Princess Mary of Denmark attended a remembrance ceremony in Denmark on Thursday .
The Tasmanian-born royal looked appropriately sombre in a chic black ensemble paired with grey accessories to mark the 75th anniversary of the occupation of Aabenraa .
The Crown Princess stepped out solo for the invasion of Denmark by Germany on April 9 , 1940 .
Queen Margarethe II was born one week later on April 16 .